Effective Date: Sept 21, 2024
KosmoNeko OÜ ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and disclose information when you use our Android application ("the App"). By using the App, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
1.
No Collection of Personal Identifiable Information (PII)
We do not collect, store, or process any Personal Identifiable Information (PII) such as your name, email address, phone number, or any other information that can be used to identify you.
2.
No Account Required
The App does not require users to create an account or log in to use its features. You can use the App without providing any personal information.
3.
Anonymous Analytics
We collect anonymous analytics to help us understand how the App is used and to improve its performance. The information collected includes:
•
Device and hardware brand information
•
Generic error reports (e.g., crashes, bugs, or malfunction logs)
This data is collected in an aggregated, anonymous form and cannot be used to identify individual users. It is solely used to improve the functionality, stability, and overall experience of the App.
4.
Third-Party Services
The App does not integrate or use any third-party services or tools that collect or share user data.
5.
Permissions
The App may request certain permissions on your Android device to function properly. However, these permissions are only used to enable features of the App and are not used to collect personal information.
6.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we do, we will revise the "Effective Date" at the top of this policy. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically to stay informed about how we protect your information.
7.
Children's Privacy
The App is not directed to children under the age of 13, and because we don’t collect any PII, we do not knowingly collect any information from children.
8.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or the App, feel free to contact us at kosmo [at] nekoko.ee.
By using the application, you agree to this Privacy Policy.